        {
            "type": "algorithm",
            "content": {
                "algorithm_caption": [],
                "algorithm_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "class Program   \n{ static void ShowVal(ref int val1, out int val2) { val1  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\equiv"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " val1; val2  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "= 0"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " ; val2  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "+ = 2"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " Console.WriteLine(\"val1  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " {val1}\"); } static void Main(string() args) { int val1  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "= 2"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " ; int val2; ShowVal(ref val1, out val2); Console.WriteLine(\"val1  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " {val1}\"); Console.WriteLine(\"val2  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " {val2}\"); Console.ReadKey(); } } "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                58,
                187,
                431,
                875
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "ref 关键字与 out 关键字的使用方式相同（在函数定义和函数调用中用作参数的修饰符）。但是，二者存在一些重要的区别："
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": " 把未赋值的变量用作 ref 参数是非法的，但是可以把未赋值的变量用作 out 参数。"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": " 另外，在函数使用 out 参数时，必须把它看成是尚未赋值。"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
